company_name: GENOSSENSCHAFT WACHOWER LANDWIRTE (GWL) E.G. OT WACHOW
information: The company GENOSSENSCHAFT WACHOWER LANDWIRTE (GWL) E.G. OT WACHOW, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1991, which operates in the Cattle industry. It also operates in the Cereals and grains industries. It is based in Nauen, Germany.
